<section
  class="relative flex min-h-[calc(100svh-108px)] flex-col items-center justify-center
         overflow-hidden px-4 pb-16 pt-16 text-center sm:px-6 sm:pb-20 sm:pt-20
         md:min-h-[calc(100svh-86px)] md:px-8 md:pt-24"
  style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 65% at 50% -10%, rgba(30,64,175,0.4) 0%, transparent 65%), radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 85% 90%, rgba(14,165,233,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%), #0a0e1a;"
>
  <!-- Headline -->
  <h1 class="hero-title mb-6">
    <span class="grad-text block" data-i18n="hero.headline1">SSH 연결부터</span>
    <span class="grad-text block" data-i18n="hero.headline2">AI 작업까지 한곳에서</span>
  </h1>

  <!-- Sub -->
  <p
    class="hero-copy mb-10 px-1 md:mb-12"
    data-i18n="hero.sub"
  >
    SSH 호스트 관리, 포트 포워딩, AI CLI 작업 흐름을 지원하는 macOS 앱
  </p>

  <!-- AI Tool Badges -->
  <div class="mb-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2.5 md:mb-12">
    {[
      { name: 'Claude Code', color: '#f97316' },
      { name: 'Codex', color: '#8b5cf6' },
      { name: 'Gemini CLI', color: '#06b6d4' },
    ].map(({ name, color }) => (
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/[0.08] bg-white/[0.03]
               px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-text-muted sm:px-3.5"
      >
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={`background:${color}`}></span>
        {name}
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <span
    class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white
           mb-5 rounded-xl px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold opacity-70 select-none
           sm:px-9 sm:py-4 sm:text-base"
    data-i18n="hero.cta"
  >
    공개 배포 준비 중
  </span>

  <!-- Meta -->
  <p
    class="text-xs text-text-darkest"
    data-i18n="hero.meta"
  >
    macOS 14.0 Sonoma 이상 · Apple Silicon & Intel
  </p>
</section>
